		(property "Description" "The ESP32-S3-DEVKITC-1-N8R8 from Espressif Systems is a development board designed for RF, RFID, and wireless applications. It supports 802.11 b/g/n Wi-Fi and Bluetooth® 5.x (BLE) connectivity at 2.4GHz, making it ideal for IoT and wireless communication projects. This board is powered by the ESP32-S3-WROOM-1-N8R8 module, which features 8MB Quad SPI Flash and 8MB Octal SPI for efficient memory storage and processing."
